data.title: 305 E Benton St. (Former Historic Masonic Temple)
data.text:
The City of Aurora, IL ("City") is requesting proposals from qualified firms ("Developers") for the acquisition, and redevelopment of the property owned at this time by the City of Aurora located at 305 E Benton St. Aurora, IL 60505 (PIN # 15-22-387-001) ("Property"). The City desires 2 single family homes residential use development. Contact Person: Purchasing Division PurchasingDL@aurora.il.us 630-256-3550 Business Hours: 8:00 am - 5:00 pm
